    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "There have been some interesting conversations over the past few years. They were philosophical and curious, yet directed and focused. These conversations have mostly been one on ones. And during a particularly beautiful sunset in Noordhoek, Julian and Leo decided that it would be interesting to try a similar format with a group of people.\n\nWe tried to define what was different about these conversations when compared to the other chit chat that happens throughout life. It was hard to pin down, but we think that it is:",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "There have been some interesting conversations over the past few years. They were philosophical and curious, yet directed and focused. These conversations have mostly been one on ones. And during a particularly beautiful sunset in Noordhoek, Julian and Leo decided that it would be interesting to try a similar format with a group of people.\n\nWe tried to define what was different about these conversations when compared to the other chit chat that happens throughout life. It was hard to pin down, but we think that it is:",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
    },
    "archived": false
  },
